WEBVTT

00:00:00.079 --> 00:00:02.496
Bahar aane
Ham ise kataar samudaay
ke lie vishist

00:00:02.579 --> 00:00:04.371
anubhav ke roop mein
sochate hain

00:00:04.371 --> 00:00:06.496
Lekin sabhee ke paas ek cheej hai

00:00:06.496 --> 00:00:08.371
jinhen ham almaree
mein rakhthe hain

00:00:08.371 --> 00:00:09.871
Hamaare paarivaar me baare

00:00:09.871 --> 00:00:11.538
maan aur shaareerik ke baare

00:00:11.538 --> 00:00:13.496
Shaayad billee se
elarjee nahin hai.

00:00:13.621 --> 00:00:15.079
aap unhen pasand nahin harate

00:00:15.079 --> 00:00:16.329
mai samajhta hun

00:00:16.329 --> 00:00:18.246
Jo kuchh bhee hai mann mein.

00:00:18.246 --> 00:00:20.579
yeh duniya ko dekhane 
ke tareeke ko deta hai

00:00:20.746 --> 00:00:23.329
Yeh aapka kaam jeevan shamil
ho saketa hai

00:00:23.329 --> 00:00:27.579
Hum in baaton ka khulaasa
kaise karate hain?

00:00:27.579 --> 00:00:30.829
Jo log hamaare paas aate hain.
.kaise sunate hain?